history.proof: intros x y z H1 H2. qsimpl time: 1 use: ge_Nge,N. qsimpl time: 1 use: ge_Nge,N. qsimpl time: 1 use: ge_Nge,N. srun best use: N.le_gt_cases, N.lt_le_trans, N.ge_le, N.le_ge unfold: N.lt, N.ge.

ctx: intros x y z H1 H2.
exceptions.exn: In environment x, y, z : N H1 : x >= z H2 : z >= y Unable to unify "(N.to_nat x >= N.to_nat z)%nat" with "x >= y".

ctx: intros x y z H1 H2.
exceptions.exn: In environment H : forall n m : nat, N.of_nat n >= N.of_nat m -> (n >= m)%nat x, y, z : N H1 : x >= z H2 : z >= y The term "H1" has type "x >= z" while it is expected to have type "z >= x" (cannot unify "(z ?= x) = Lt" and "(x ?= z) = Lt").

ctx: intros x y z H1 H2.
exceptions.exn: In environment H0 : forall n m : nat, N.of_nat n >= N.of_nat m -> (n >= m)%nat x, y, z : N H1 : x >= z H2 : z >= y Unable to unify "y <= x" with "x >= y".

ctx: intros x y z H1 H2.
exceptions.exn: The reference ge_Nge_rev was not found in the current environment.

original: intros x y z H1 H2. apply (ge_Nge (N.to_nat x) (N.to_nat z)). apply (N.ge_le z x H1). apply (N.ge_le x y). apply (ge_Nge_rev x z H2).
